#: ../../reference/customize.rst:121
msgid ""
"pytest determines a ``rootdir`` for each test run which depends on the "
"command line arguments (specified test files, paths) and on the existence"
" of configuration files.  The determined ``rootdir`` and ``configfile`` "
"are printed as part of the pytest header during startup."
