#: ../../reference/customize.rst:139
msgid ""
"The ``--rootdir=path`` command-line option can be used to force a "
"specific directory. Note that contrary to other command-line options, "
"``--rootdir`` cannot be used with :confval:`addopts` inside "
"``pytest.ini`` because the ``rootdir`` is used to *find* ``pytest.ini`` "
